Design a 4-input AND gate with an enable signal. The module takes four inputs (A1, A2, A3, A4) and an enable signal (EN). When EN is asserted, the output Y will be HIGH only if all four inputs are HIGH; otherwise, Y will be LOW.
module top_module(
    output Y,
    input A1,
    input A2,
    input A3,
    input A4,
    input EN
);

**原始代码**：
```verilog
module top_module(
    output Y,
    input A1,
    input A2,
    input A3,
    input A4,
    input EN
);wire [3:0] inputs;
    wire and_output;

    // Assign the inputs to a vector
    assign inputs = {A4, A3, A2, A1};

    // Perform AND operation on inputs and include enable
    assign and_output = (EN) ? (inputs[3] & inputs[2] & inputs[1] & inputs[0]) : 1'b0;

    // Assign the result to Y
    assign Y = and_output;

endmodule
```

**功能规范**：
Implement a 16-bit wide custom counter with load and reset functionality. When the clock signal's positive edge is detected, the counter will reset to zero if the reset input is high. If the load input is high, it will load the value from `loadValue`. The counter increments on every clock cycle, and upon reaching its maximum value (all bits high), it wraps around to zero. Additionally, a flag output indicates when the counter has reached its maximum value.
module top_module(
   input         clock, reset, load,
   input [15:0]  loadValue,
   output [15:0] count,
   output        flag);

**原始代码**：
```verilog
module top_module(
   input         clock, reset, load,
   input [15:0]  loadValue,
   output [15:0] count,
   output        flag);reg [15:0]    countReg = 16'b0;
   wire          flagWire;

   assign flag = flagWire;
   assign count = countReg;

   always @ (posedge clock) begin 
      if (reset)
         countReg <= 16'b0;
      else if (load)
         countReg <= loadValue;
      else if (countReg == {16{1'b1}})
         countReg <= 16'b0;
      else
         countReg <= countReg + 1;
   end

   assign flagWire = (countReg == {16{1'b1}});

endmodule
```

