**功能规范**：
Develop a circuit that functions as a four-input comparator. The module evaluates the inputs A1, A2, A3, and B1 to determine the output Y: it outputs a logic LOW when all inputs are LOW (0000), a logic HIGH when all inputs are HIGH (1111), and outputs a logic HIGH for any combination of inputs that is not all LOW, while conversely outputting a logic LOW for any combination that does not represent all HIGH. If the inputs cannot be uniquely classified into these categories, the output is left in an unknown state.
